No. 10-8055. Richard F. Mills, Petitioner v. New York. 562 U.S. 1211, 131 S. Ct. 1504,

179 L. Ed. 2d 294,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 1128. February 22, 2011.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the County Court of New York, Genesee County, dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
